Colonial Oil Hires John Spencer to Start Geneva Trading Office

-- B y   L a n a n h   N g u y e n
-- 
2011-04-04T08:18:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-04/colonial-oil-hires-john-spencer-to-start-geneva-trading-office.html
Colonial Oil Industries Inc.  hired
John Spencer to start a fuel supply and trading office in
Geneva, the company said in an e-mailed statement.  “Spencer will be active in light and heavy products in
European and Baltic markets,” the Savannah, Georgia-based unit
of Colonial Group Inc. said on April 1. The company sells
wholesale and retail petroleum products.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lananh Nguyen in London at 
 lnguyen35@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss on   sev@bloomberg.net  